I could've gone to a real doctor

256
00:13:25,971 --> 00:13:28,807
instead of pretending I was a big dog,
so I could go to the vet.

257
00:13:30,476 --> 00:13:32,895
You know, that gives me an idea,

258
00:13:33,604 --> 00:13:37,149
