to transfer the totality of your account,

264
00:13:50,538 --> 00:13:55,709
131 million British pounds,
to the account of this person,

265
00:13:56,669 --> 00:14:01,173
a man who is so flagrantly ignoring
the "one lollipop per customer" rule.

266
00:14:01,257 --> 00:14:04,760
No. I walked out and back in each time,
so I'm different customers.

267
00:14:05,553 --> 00:14:07,680
We're technically
supposed to shut down the bank

268
00:14:07,763 --> 00:14:10,266
if anyone from Florida even walks in.

269
00:14:10,349 --> 00:14:14,061
Look, all my life, this money
has been a weight around my neck.

270
00:14:14,144 --> 00:14:16,897
Like the Heart of the Ocean necklace
my friend James Cameron once gave me.

271
00:14:17,565 --> 00:14:19,692
