My friend Jason does.

272
00:14:19,775 --> 00:14:21,277
I would like to give it to him.

273
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:24,029
If it's easier, you can just put it
on a GameStop gift card.

274
00:14:24,613 --> 00:14:28,826
That does not make it easier.
I can't help you. I'm sorry.

275
00:14:32,621 --> 00:14:33,581
-Good day.
-[Eleanor] Fred?

276
00:14:33,664 --> 00:14:36,041
My name is Eleanor Shellstrop.
I have all your crap.

277
00:14:37,585 --> 00:14:38,460
[Fred] Thank you.

278
00:14:39,044 --> 00:14:40,045
[Eleanor] And your wallet.

279
00:14:40,129 --> 00:14:43,465
Oh, my goodness! Thank you so much.

280
00:14:43,549 --> 00:14:44,383
It was nothing.

281
00:14:45,426 --> 00:14:48,470
Dude, I didn't take your money.
I would never even think of doing that.

282
00:14:48,554 --> 00:14:50,306
No, no, no. I'm not worried about that.

283
00:14:50,848 --> 00:14:52,641
Ah! Here it is.

284
00:14:54,393 --> 00:14:57,771
{\an8}I started a new job a few months ago
and I got really nervous,

285
00:14:57,855 --> 00:15:01,442
so my daughter Carolyn drew this for me
to make me feel better.

286
00:15:01,525 --> 00:15:03,193
It's my good luck charm.

287
00:15:03,277 --> 00:15:06,530
Every time I'm stressed at work now,
I just have to look at this,

288
00:15:06,614 --> 00:15:08,657
and I feel safe.

289
00:15:09,408 --> 00:15:13,037
Look, a lot of people wouldn't have
tried so hard to get this to me.

290
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:14,788
You are a good person, Eleanor.

291
00:15:15,414 --> 00:15:17,666
I really hope my daughter
turns out like you when she grows up.

292
00:15:19,668 --> 00:15:22,046
-You all right?
-No, you shut up!

293
00:15:22,838 --> 00:15:24,673
Sorry. It's been a weird day.

294
00:15:27,176 --> 00:15:29,303
[Chidi] ♪ <i>You put the Peeps</i>
