told me to do something good today,

383
00:20:09,249 --> 00:20:12,669
and it was so annoying,
but it also made a dork

384
00:20:12,753 --> 00:20:14,922
and his very untalented daughter
super happy.

385
00:20:15,839 --> 00:20:19,676
Me trying, just a little bit,
put some good out into the world.

386
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:23,138
The six of us
are not getting into the Good Place,

387
00:20:23,222 --> 00:20:26,600
but there are still people in this world
that we care about.

388
00:20:26,683 --> 00:20:30,562
So I say, we try and help them
be good people,

389
00:20:30,646 --> 00:20:33,398
try and help them get in.
I mean, why not try?

390
00:20:33,482 --> 00:20:35,275
It's better than not trying, right?

391
00:20:35,359 --> 00:20:40,072
That's a lovely sentiment, Eleanor.
Let's try. I'm in.

392
00:20:40,155 --> 00:20:41,156
{\an8}I'm in, too.

393
00:20:41,698 --> 00:20:44,368
{\an8}I'm gonna remember this day forever
because of your dope speech.

394
00:20:44,451 --> 00:20:47,704
{\an8}And also because of the great tacos I had,
and also because I got married,

395
00:20:47,788 --> 00:20:50,916
{\an8}and I found out I was going to hell,
