00:20:56,838 --> 00:20:57,798
{\an8}All right, you go.

400
00:20:57,881 --> 00:20:59,174
{\an8}-We're in.
-We're in. [chuckles]

401
00:20:59,258 --> 00:21:01,385
{\an8}-We're just so excited!
-We're in!

402
00:21:02,219 --> 00:21:03,178
{\an8}What do you say, bud?

403
00:21:03,262 --> 00:21:06,431
{\an8}You wanna join the Soul Squad?
