404
00:21:07,015 --> 00:21:09,101
{\an8}-Yeah, I'm in.
-[sighs]

405
00:21:09,184 --> 00:21:12,437
{\an8}But first, I have to go
to the bathroom forever.

406
00:21:13,438 --> 00:21:14,606
